item.title: How do we measure change?
item.description: Many website operators have been receiving warning letters for some time now. The transfer of personal data - the plaintiff’s IP address - to Google , due to the dynamic linking of Google Fonts, is the accusation. If you have received such a letter, stay calm and inform yourself in detail before you get upset. The situation is not as threatening as it appears at first glance. Most of the letters currently emerging are obviously mass mailings that come from two people:
